descriptionHtml:
They are the Spawn of the Daedra,Half Mortal and half Daedric prince, the Daedric princes Brutally ????? female mortals, so they can create their Champion and spread seeds of Chaos and dispair across the mortal plane,many Evil, barley any are good 

Abilities and Powers are 
Supernatural Inferno 
Ether Telekinesis 
Daedric Blood which is your resistances to Magic(100%), Damage(50%), Poison & Disease (100%) 
Daedric Explosion-at the snap of your fingers, a mortal explodes 
Daedric Rage 
Night eye 
Daedric Immortality 
Daedric Control (control Npc's for 2 mintues at a time) 
Daedric Demigod Breathing (Your Demigod lungs can breath underwater.)
Daedric Explosion (at the snap of your fingers, a mortal explodes)
Daedric Summon (you are able to summon a Dremora Lord for 1 day.)
Daedric Energy Blasts (you are able to throw energy blasts at your foes)

Custom Red Glowing Eyes textures 


Enjoy everyone
author: KalEltheKryptonian and Elia
